Replace bash-4.3$ with user@host path (Changing promt env variable)
-------------------------------------------------------------------

For bash
export PS1='[\u@\h \w] '



For tcsh
export prompt='[%n@%m %~] '



for zsh
export PS1='[%n@%m %~] '


https://superuser.com/questions/68397/why-does-my-linux-prompt-show-a-instead-of-the-login-name-and-path
